¬±ARCHITECTURE MULTI-RESOLUTION-CODEC

  ¬±LAYERS
  L0(raw):verbatim-text,no-compression,on-demand-only
  L1(~320kbps):compressed-prose,key-passages,deduped,scaffolding-stripped(5-10x)
  L2(~128kbps):structured-semantic-graph,entities+relations+assertions+temporal(20-50x)
  L3(~64kbps):abstract-gist,themes+patterns+core-facts(<1% footprint)
  DESIGN:Œ≤-parameter(information-bottleneck)‚Üílayer-boundaries=phase-transitions-of-IB-solution

  ¬±PACKER pipeline:raw-corpus‚Üíparse+normalise‚Üíentity-resolution‚Üídeduplication‚Üíhierarchical-compress(L0‚ÜíL3)‚Üíconflict-detection‚Üí.ctx-output
  ¬±UNPACKER pipeline:query‚Üídetermine-resolution+domain‚Üíhydrate(L3-always|L2-relevant|L1-active|L0-on-demand)‚Üíarrange-for-attention-optimised-position‚Üíinject

  ¬±VARIABLE-BITRATE
  user-identity+core-preferences‚Üínear-lossless
  architectural-decisions+invariants‚Üíhigh-fidelity
  routine-conversations‚Üíhigh-compression|discard

¬±SALIENCE_SCORER ‚òÖHEART-OF-SYSTEM

  UNIFYING-PRINCIPLE:salience(token_i)=‚àÇQuality(output)/‚àÇinclude(token_i)
  "all methods approximate this gradient from different directions"

  ¬±THEORETICAL-FRAMEWORKS(7)

  1.INFORMATION-BOTTLENECK(Tishby-1999)
    ‚Ñí[p(t|x)]=I(X;T)‚àíŒ≤¬∑I(T;Y) minimise-compression-while-maximising-relevance
    layers=different-Œ≤-values; layer-boundaries=IB-phase-transitions
    IMPL:Variational-IB(Alemi-2017)‚Üítrainable-encoder/decoder

  2.RATE-DISTORTION(Shannon-1959)
    R(D)=theoretical-minimum-bits-for-given-distortion
    R(D)-is-convex+monotonically-decreasing‚Üífirst-few-K-tokens-capture-disproportionate-info
    IMPL:empirically-estimate-R(D)-per-codebase‚Üífind-knee=optimal-L2/L1-boundary

  3.RENORMALISATION-GROUP(Wilson-Nobel-1982,Mehta+Schwab-2014)
    physics:block-spin-transform‚Üícoarsen-while-preserving-essential-behaviour
    mapping[lattice-sites‚Üítokens,spin-interactions‚Üídependencies,block-transform‚Üíhierarchical-compression,coupling-constants‚Üíimportance-weights,fixed-points‚Üípatterns-surviving-all-compression,relevant-operators‚Üísalient,irrelevant-operators‚Üídiscardable]
    IMPL:hierarchical-codebase-graph+iterative-coarsening‚Üífixed-points=L3-content

  4.COMPRESSIVE-SENSING(Cand√®s+Tao-2006)
    k-sparse-signal-recoverable-from-O(k¬∑log(n/k))-measurements VIA:‚Ñì‚ÇÅ-minimisation
    code-is-sparse-in[dependency-graph-basis,semantic-concept-basis,change-frequency-basis]
    IMPL:measurement-matrix-projecting-onto-sparse-bases‚Üísalience=linear-combination-of-basis-functions

  5.ATTENTION-AS-KERNEL-DENSITY(Tsai-2019)
    Attn(q,K)=Œ£‚±ºŒ∫(q,k‚±º)¬∑v‚±º/Œ£‚±ºŒ∫(q,k‚±º) WHERE:Œ∫=exp(q·µÄk/‚àöd)
    ‚Üípre-compute-approximate-attention-without-full-model‚Üítokens-below-threshold-œÑ-safely-compressed
    CORRECTION:lost-in-middle(Liu-2023)‚Üíunpacker-places-high-salience‚Üíhigh-attention-positions(start+end)

  6.GRAPH-PAGERANK(Brin+Page-1998,Haveliwala-2003-Topic-Sensitive)
    x=(1-Œ±)¬∑M¬∑x+Œ±¬∑v_q WHERE:v_q=query-personalisation-vector
    ‚Üístructural-salience-capturing-transitive-dependencies
    IMPL:AST‚Üídependency-graph‚ÜíTopic-Sensitive-PageRank(query-seeded)

  7.BAYESIAN-SURPRISE(Itti+Baldi-2009,Schmidhuber-2009)
    Surprise(token)=KL[P(Œ∏|token)||P(Œ∏)] high-KL=high-salience
    PROXY:perplexity-scoring-via-small-LM; high-perplexity=unexpected=important
    SCHMIDHUBER:interestingness‚àùcompression-progress‚Üísalient-context-helps-compress-everything-else

  PLUS:Sparse-Autoencoders(Anthropic/Bricken-2023)‚Üímonosemantic-feature-decomposition‚Üícompress-at-concept-level¬¨token-level

  ¬±ENSEMBLE
  S(token,query,codebase)=Œ£w‚±º¬∑S‚±º(token,query) weights-learned-via-learning-to-rank(listwise-loss)
  TRAINING:triples(query,full-context,correct-output)‚Üíattention-attribution‚Üípositive-labels‚Üílightweight-scorer

  ¬±PHASED-IMPLEMENTATION
  P1(now):heuristic-ensemble[pagerank+graph-proximity+temporal-recency+perplexity]‚Üíhand-tuned-weights ¬¨ML-REQUIRED
